properties.headline: Small Craft Advisory issued January 8 at 2:39PM CST until January 10 at 3:00AM CST by NWS Milwaukee/Sullivan WI
properties.description:
* WHAT...Southeast winds to 25 kt shifting south by late Thursday
morning and southwest for Thursday evening. Gusts approaching
gale force. Waves building to 7 to 12 feet by sunrise.

* WHERE...Sheboygan to Winthrop Harbor IL.

* WHEN...From midnight tonight to 3 AM CST Friday.

* IMPACTS...Conditions will be hazardous to small craft.
properties.instruction:
Inexperienced mariners, especially those operating smaller
vessels, should avoid navigating in hazardous conditions.

NWSheadline: SMALL CRAFT ADVISORY IN EFFECT FROM MIDNIGHT TONIGHT TO 3 AM CST FRIDAY
